            <h4>Art and Music have been an integral part of our curriculum as they meet the creative needs of a child. It gives children freedom to express themselves. Children tend to relate better to such creative endeavors and man a times produce commendable work. This sets the stage for learning other subjects well, while discreetly boosting their confidence.<br><br>

International Music Day is celebrated at Young Hearts every year with many schools participating vying to clinch various awards. </h4>
