            <h4>It's understood that mental prowess is reliant on physical growth and development. With this in mind, we lay equal emphasis on the need for regular sports and sport-related activities. This is not merely confined to games like basketball and football, but even other games which may require children to use judgement, tactics and reasoning. Games like chess and various other board games are also encouraged. </h4>
