            <h4>The school has a reputed paediatrician / physician who visits the school every Saturday for check-ups. Children are given medications only on the doctor's recommendation. The school charges a nominal annual fee as medical fees. Apart from the general medications and treatments, cases that may require specialized care and long term treatment / therapy or long term courses will be billed by the school or may be followed up by the parents in consultation with the school. </h4>
